# AuthController - Authentication endpoints

### Register
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "0123456789"
}

### Login
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Logout (requires token)
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Forgot password
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### Reset password
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset-token",
  "password": "new-password"
}
